    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example of automotive excellence. Finished in a deep, lustrous metallic paint that has been protected by a professional ceramic coating since day one, the exterior is absolutely flawless\u2014free of swirl marks, stone chips, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, retaining that fresh, factory-new scent. The premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear, and every piece of cabin technology, from the high-fidelity surround sound to the touch-sensitive displays, functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively maintained at authorized dealerships, with a complete, documented service history confirming every scheduled inspection and fluid change. The engine bay is immaculate, and the high-performance tires have nearly full tread depth. Always kept in a climate-controlled garage and never driven in inclement weather, this car represents the absolute pinnacle of its model year.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
