    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to an uncompromising standard. This vehicle represents the zenith of automotive preservation, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior environment that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. For the collector or discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this offering provides a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled integrity and distinction.",
      "price": 48500.0,
