      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it! It's been my absolute pride and joy, kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed every single week. It looks and drives exactly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single mark on it and it still has that brand-new smell! I'm only letting it go to make some space, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44900.0,
